                     <interp inst="t18070408-3-off15" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070408-3-off15" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18070408-3-victim73" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
