                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070408-3-off15 t18070408-3-cd16"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, two silver table spoons, value 30 s. four silver tea spoons, value 12 s. a gold broach, value 2 s. a gold pin, value 2 s. and a gold ring, value 3 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18070408-3-person74">
                        Charles 
